<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?vid=l3053920tyn&amp;auto=0&amp;width=500px&amp;height=375px"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>肝脏是人体担任消化和代谢的主要器官。只有它正常工作，我们的身体才能正常运转，及时排毒。</span><span>今天就给大家介绍几种比较常见的肝脏解毒王，每周吃一次，给肝脏祛毒，给血管洗澡~</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>牛蒡</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>牛蒡，有“东洋参”之美称。</span><span>含有很多牛蒡甙和木脂素，其间牛蒡甙元是抗癌活性物质，能一面扫除人体毒素，一面以营养成分进行补养和调度，养肝非常好。</span></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200801/dd15f0b88431422e859bf873d3bb29eb.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>干品泡茶</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>给肝脏排毒，给血管洗澡</strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>【用法】</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">取干的牛蒡片6~10克，以沸水泡之，频饮。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>白萝卜</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>白萝卜被称为是“小人参”，它自带解毒功效，是对肝脏极好的一种食物，可有效提高肝功能。</span><span>另外，白萝卜对于酒精中毒有奇效，它可以帮助乙醛分解，是养肝护肝的圣品。</span></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>白萝卜+豆腐</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>低热量高蛋白，肝脏血管都喜爱</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>【做法】</strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">白萝卜和生姜切片备用，豆腐切成块备用。</span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">把切好的白萝卜和生姜，加入水中煮沸，待水沸后转小火。</span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">等白萝卜基本煮软后，加入豆腐</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">，继续炖煮5～10分钟，加入少许调料调味。</span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">撒上葱花，即可出锅。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>葛根</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">葛根是很好的护肝食品，对脂肪肝、酒精肝都有很好的康复作用。葛根粉当中含有大量的大豆甙，可以加速酒精分解，减少其对于大脑和肝脏的伤害、对肠胃的刺激。</span></p>
<p><span>...........................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>陈皮葛根茶</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>保肝健脾，理气化湿</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>【做法】</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">取葛根、陈皮干品等份，以沸水冲泡，盖上盖子闷泡15分钟即可，可以反复冲泡至味淡。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>荞麦米</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">荞麦米在五谷中具有较高的食用价值跟要用价值。其性甘，味凉，含有的烟酸成分可以帮助促进机体的新陈代谢，增强肝脏的排毒能力。</span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>荞麦杂粮饭</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>完善营养，延年益寿</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>【做法】</strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">将荞麦提前用温水泡上2～4个小时。将大米和泡好的荞麦一同放入电饭锅中，添水，煮饭即可。</span><span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>乌梅</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">乌梅不仅生津解渴，还能加强肝脏的解毒能力、促进消化吸收。《黄帝内经》中记载“酸入肝”，乌梅味酸，对肝脏有益处。 <span>...................................................................................................................................</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>乌梅冰糖饮</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>护肝解暑，引火归元</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>【做法】</strong></span></p>
<p><span>...................................................................................................................................</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">乌梅9克（或3个）、山楂9克、冰糖适量、盐1克、水适量。</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">泡半小时，大火烧开，小火再煮30~50分钟。</span><span></span></p>
